{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/react/usestate-만들어보기/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ka0824's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3030d868-b134-5a29-9cda-c4ca4ebe1058","excerpt":"학습내용 문득 평소 사용하고 있는 useState가 어떻게 구성되어 있을지 궁금해져서 직접 만들어 보려 하였다. 우선 useState의 형태를 생각하면 만들어 본 코드이다. 평소 사용하듯이 input태그에 적용해본 결과 다음과 같은 문제점이 있었다. state…","html":"<blockquote>\n<h2>학습내용</h2>\n</blockquote>\n<p>문득 평소 사용하고 있는 useState가 어떻게 구성되어 있을지 궁금해져서 직접 만들어 보려 하였다.</p>\n<p>우선 useState의 형태를 생각하면 만들어 본 코드이다. 평소 사용하듯이 input태그에 적용해본 결과 다음과 같은 문제점이 있었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>selfUseState<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">selfUseState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">initialState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> initialState<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">setState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nextState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nextState<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setState<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>state의 변화는 받아올 수 있다. (console.log를 통해 값을 입력할 때마다 state 값이 변화함을 알 수 있다.)</li>\n<li>그러나 값이 변화함에도 리렌더링이 되지 않는다.</li>\n<li>따라서, setState 함수 내에서 리렌더링을 하게끔하는 동작을 추가해야 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>문제를 해결하기 위해 찾아본 리렌더링을 할 수 있는 방법들이다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>임의의 값을 useState로 관리하여 리렌더링이 필요할 때마다 변화시켜준다. (&#x3C;- useState 구현을 위해 useState를 사용해야한다는 오류가 있다.)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>클래스형 컴포넌트의 forceUpdate를 사용한다. (&#x3C;- 함수형 컴포넌트에서도 구현이 되어 있는지, 사용할 방법이 있는지 찾을 수 없었다.)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>ReactDOM.render()를 사용한다.(&#x3C;- 현재 사용하고 있는 react18버전에서는 사용할 수 없다며 오류가 발생한다.)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>index.js에 있는 코드를 활용해 리렌더링을 시도해 본다. (&#x3C;- 시도해본 방법이다.)</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>index<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom/client\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./index.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> App <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./App\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> reportWebVitals <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./reportWebVitals\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> root <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createRoot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nroot<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>StrictMode<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>App <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>StrictMode<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>selfUseState<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom/client\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">selfUseState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">initialState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> initialState<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">setState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nextState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nextState<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n       <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> root <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createRoot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n       root<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>App <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setState<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>index.js에 있는 코드를 그대로 옮겨온 결과 콘솔창에서 에러 메시지를 확인할 수 있었다. 대략 root를 이미 선언 했는데,\n또 선언하려 하지 말아라 인듯 하다. 그래서 root를 새로 선언하지 말고 index.js에서 가져오는 방식으로 바꾸었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>selfUseState<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom/client\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> root <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./index\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">selfUseState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">initialState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> initialState<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">setState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nextState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nextState<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n       root<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>App <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setState<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>해당 코드로 바꾼 결과, 이번에는 아무리 값을 바꾸어도 값이 안 바뀌는 현상이 발생했다. 이 현상은 리렌더링을 추가한 이후\n발생하였던 것으로 보아, 리렌더링이 될 때 selfUseState 함수도 재실행되면서 state 값이 initialState 값으로 계속해서\n재할당되는 것으로 파악됐다. 따라서, 함수가 재실행되더라도 값이 유지될 수 있도록, 함수 외부에서 변수를 선언해주었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>selfUseState<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom/client\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> root <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./index\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> state<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">selfUseState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">initialState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">undefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> initialState     <span class=\"token comment\">// state 값이 undefined일 때만, 초기 값을 할당해준다.</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">setState</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nextState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nextState<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n       root<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>App <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setState<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>이제는 입력한 값을 저장하고, 값이 변할 때마다 재랜더링을 하여 화면에 보이는 값을 동기화할 수 있었다.\n물론, 실제 useState 훅은 더 많은 최적화 과정을 거치겠지만, 그 외에 현재 selfUseState의 한계는 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>index.js에서 root를 가져와야 한다.</li>\n<li>selfUseState를 다른 파일에서 관리하면 재랜더링을 하기 위해 해당 컴포넌트의 정보를 받아와야만 한다. props로\n컴포넌트를 넘겨줄 수 있을지라도, 그렇다면 기존 useState 훅 보다 많은 인자를 필요로 하게 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>현재의 한계들은 모두 재랜더링을 어떻게 하느냐에 따라 해결 가능해질 수도 있지 않을까 싶다. 리액트가 랜더링 되는 조건 외에도\n랜더링을 어떻게 이루어지나에 대한 학습이 필요할 듯하다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<h2>참고하면 좋은 자료</h2>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_qkX3yAmgEw\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_qkX3yAmgEw</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"useState 만들어보기","date":"June 08, 2022","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/network/ip-인터넷-프로토콜/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"IP 인터넷 프로토콜"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/TIL/2022.06.08-til/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"2022.06.08-TIL"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"3030d868-b134-5a29-9cda-c4ca4ebe1058","previousPostId":"f904af40-cce1-5d2e-8f04-b0593a9e2523","nextPostId":"9af91763-48f6-52cb-afc4-83793fd5cf98"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}